INTEL多啲？</blockquote><br />\n我上網睇 話偏向打機用intel好會少少 所以就揀i7</blockquote><br />\n打開144MHz？係就無問題 唔係我可以笑下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴打有冇推介 主要係打機同睇戲 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n打開144mhz追求極致一兩年後換機咪i7<br />\n打60mhz ryzen1700夠做有凸啦 平台仲要平啲 八核點都耐玩過四核 講到口臭<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n到最後一定要i7 等多陣啦 intel好快會出新一代i7 不過你預算啲老母板會好L貴"},{"pid":"192cfc1fde73baf7fefad6c9168efd6ccfa030aa","tid":256094,"uid":29885,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T13:30:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>其實我覺得轉AMD好少少嘅，唔知你係咪鍾意INTEL多啲？</blockquote><br />\n我上網睇 話偏向打機用intel好會少少 所以就揀i7</blockquote><br />\n打開144MHz？係就無問題 唔係我可以笑下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴打有冇推介 主要係打機同睇戲 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n打開144mhz追求極致一兩年後換機咪i7<br />\n打60mhz ryzen1700夠做有凸啦 平台仲要平啲 八核點都耐玩過四核 講到口臭<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n到最後一定要i7 等多陣啦 intel好快會出新一代i7 不過你預算啲老母板會好L貴</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n明白 唔該巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71593524a934a5b614534a45ee34a10f0d25a68a","tid":256094,"uid":48022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T14:18:53.000Z","msg":"144MHz<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n量子電腦咁快都冇"},{"pid":"e0f020fb72f378d881cc8c12ee7a1e44bf0f0d7a","tid":256094,"uid":82489,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T14:21:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>144MHz<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n量子電腦咁快都冇</blockquote><br />\n條友痴左線<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/24.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7156867b28e76ae905dbe464acdc