faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n佢轉左cpu同底板<br />\n就算升1080印象應該夠<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n當然佢如果仲有唔知咩其他額外硬件就另記<br />\n<br />\n不過都唔樓主想點玩法，要追求性能極限定性格比<br />\n見佢用7700k就諗住7700<br />\n轉個頭比人講兩講就轉amd(ps:我將來新機都選用amd)<br />\n不如樓主你講清楚你諗住點玩法<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n另外如果你個mon廢既話1080用唔到就搞笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc37543df20959c25511e737a8a7ee18023399ff","tid":256094,"uid":81059,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T15:52:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>其實我覺得轉AMD好少少嘅，唔知你係咪鍾意INTEL多啲？</blockquote><br />\n我上網睇 話偏向打機用intel好會少少 所以就揀i7</blockquote><br />\n打開144MHz？係就無問題 唔係我可以笑下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴打有冇推介 主要係打機同睇戲 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n打開144mhz追求極致一兩年後換機咪i7<br />\n打60mhz ryzen1700夠做有凸啦 平台仲要平啲 八核點都耐玩過四核 講到口臭<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n到最後一定要i7 等多陣啦 intel好快會出新一代i7 不過你預算啲老母板會好L貴</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n再唔係等intel出完新，平價入返7700<br />\n雖然低能，但性價比應該幾高<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"82716e4e0b4384af538a4c44dfb19275a10e9ef0","tid":256094,"uid":83102,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-24T16:11:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>其實我覺得轉AMD好少少嘅，唔知你係咪鍾意INTEL多啲？</blockquote><br />\n我上網睇 話偏向打機用intel好會少少 所以就揀i7</blockquote><br />\n打開144MHz？係就無問題 唔係我可以笑下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n巴打有冇推介 主要係打機同睇戲 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n打開144mhz追求極致一兩年後換機咪i7<br />\n打60mhz ryzen1700夠做有凸啦 平台仲要平啲 八核點都耐玩過四核 講到口臭<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n到最後一定要i7 等多陣啦 intel好快會出新一代i7 不過你預算啲老母板會好L貴</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n再唔係等intel出完新，平價入返7700<br />\n雖然低能，但性價比應該幾高<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n點會低價入到呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}